item.title: Feeling Alone!
item.dc:creator: prisonmike
item.description: I am sorry everyone. I wanted to add every one of my friends to this blog, but Jan didn’t let me. So, other employees who were added to this blog are now removed. As of now there is only one user in this blog. Which is me! Just me.
item.content:encoded:
I am sorry everyone. I wanted to add every one of my friends to this blog, but Jan didn’t let me.

So, other employees who were added to this blog are now removed.

As of now there is only one user in this blog. Which is me! Just me.

item.title: Secret of my success
item.dc:creator: prisonmike
item.description: Don’t ever, for any reason, do anything to anyone for any reason ever, no matter what, no matter where, or who, or who you are with, or where you are going, or where you’ve been… ever, for any reason whatsoever…
